    <h1><em>Boyhood</em> takes home Best Film prize at BAFTA Awards</h1>
    
          <p class="byline">
        by <a href="/author/ariana-bacle">Ariana Bacle </a>         &bull; <span class="twitter"><a href="https://twitter.com/iambacle">@iambacle</a></span>      </p>
